text: Diamond Foods was an American packaged food company based in San Francisco. It marketed nuts (particularly walnuts and almonds) and other snack foods. It was founded in 1912. Itwas acquired by Snyder's-Lance in 2016, and as of 2018, Campbell Soup Company owns Diamond Foods's former snack brands.
